essible parking for customers and for take out needs  we are extremely pleased by the progress we have made since opening our first location in river oaks said federico marques vpmarketing and cofounder  our citycentre location is the only star certified green restaurant® in texas and one of the greenest restaurants in the world  our sugar land location will be star certified and will maintain the quality of food and customer experience we are known for  our goal is to expand our childrens healthy organic and glutenfree menu options and to continuously improve our sustainability model  it is very gratifying to see the positive response to our ruggles green vision which has allowed us to push forward with two new locations robert guillerman vpoperations and cofounder states our customers have expectations of high quality food at an affordable price with excellent service  our confidence lies in our employees and in the experience we have gained over the last three years  we look forward to servicing more neighborhoods in the greater houston area and also in becoming a valued part of those communities  we realize that every customer has unique needs and we work hard to ensure we live up and hopefully exceed their expectations  jennifer mcgehee vp gjr partnership commented our affiliation with green cafe management was formed to provide the financial support they needed to expand the ruggles green franchise  we are pleased to be associated with our ruggles green partners and to support their vision and leadership in the green restaurant movement moreover we look forward to providing the capital and support for the new heights and sugar land locations ruggles green is a certified green restaurant® and conforms to guidelines set by the green restaurant association ruggles green has completed an incredible amount of steps towards becoming more environmentally sustainable says jennifer fleck communications manager for the gra ruggles green is not only the greenest restaurant in texas but one of the greenest in the world they set a wonderful example for the industry and we look forward to going even further with them in the future about ruggles green formed in  ruggles green is houstons first certified green restaurant® in  ruggles green at citycentre also became the first star certified green restaurant in texas the green restaurant associations highest level of certification ruggles green was launched with the goal of providing local organic and gluten free options to customers via a premium fast casual restaurant  the vision of the founders was to lead the industry in sustainability while still offering healthy and great tasting food  federico marques and robert guillerman are cofounders and are responsible for the operations of the business ruggles green stores conform to guidelines set by the green restaurant association  guidelines include energy conservation water conservation extensive recycling composting use of sustainable materials public education and outreach and use of local organic and vegetarian menu items  green cafe management owns ruggles green  for more information visit wwwrugglesgreencom about gjr partnership the gjr partnership was formed by a group of houston and calgarybased investors to provide the financial and general management to support the ruggles green expansion in houston  the partnership has a management and license agreement with green cafe management for the rights to own multiple ruggles green restaurants and for green cafe management to provide the instore operations jennifer mcgehee is a vp and partner of gjr partnership and is gjrs houstonbased operations and marketing executive about the green restaurant association the green restaurant association gra a national nonprofit organization helps the restaurant industry improve its environmental practices through research environmental consulting education and certification founded in  long before green was cool the gra utilizes a collaborative strategy that involves restaurants manufacturers vendors community organizations government media and restaurant customers for more information visit wwwdinegreencom contact federico marques email federicomrugglesgreencom phone  source ruggles green restaurant related links httpwwwrugglesgreencom view table fullscreen view table fullscreen journalists and bloggers the news you need when you need it join pr newswire for journalists to access all of the free services designated to make your job easier in need of subject matter experts for your story submit a free profnet request and find the sources you need learn more mar    et preview ruggles green joins kids livewell™ my news release contains wide tables view fullscreen looking to send a news release with pr newswire take advantage of the worlds leading distribution platform sign up to get started request more information have an account log in search searching for your content advanced search microsoft personalized ad preferences to opt out of personalized ads in this browser your browser history must allow firstparty and thirdparty cookies and you must have your browsing experience set to not delete browsing history on exit instructions for enabling cookies and configuring your browsing history may be available in your browsers settings privacy or help documentation sign in hold on… we’re sorry but this didn’t work you can’t turn off personalized ads right now because your browser is currently blocking thirdparty cookies we can help you fix this issue let’s get started depending on what browser you use open options or settings make sure that thirdparty cookies are not blocked anymore to find out how search your browser’s help revisit httpchoicemicrosoftcomoptout and then on the “personalized ads in this browser” tile click off ext about our ads to create a more customized online experience some of the ads you may receive on microsoft websites and apps are tailored to your previous activities searches and site visits